root: ^What's going on? Do you not remember me?
^Are you the one I talked to on the phone.
^I mean... we talked on the phone a while ago, I think.
^Yeah, we've been waiting for you for hours.
^I don't want to talk about it.
^Junior Ring Master. Reginald was the Head Ring Master, but he was... He's gone now.
^There was another Ring Master? I don't remember a Reginald.
